The festive fixtures in the Premier League continue this weekend. The early kick-off will see Bournemouth travel to Brighton. Norwich City host Tottenham Hotspur, while Leicester City are away to West Ham. Manchester United clash with Burnley at Turf Moor in the last fixture of Saturday. Saturday, December 28
